      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，PaymentGateway作为入口。那TransactionQueue在中间层，它和AuthVault之间是什么关系？我注意到可能有双向交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
