    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出PaymentGateway指向TransactionQueue，然后加上双向的AuthVault连接，还有FraudDetection指向TransactionQueue的审计链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
