    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，FraudDetection应该是从TransactionQueue接收信号，而不是主动指向队列。还有，Risk模块和Signal节点也需要放进去，它们处理实时风控决策。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
